 3. the person eating pumpkin is between the person eating lettuce and the person driving the train##2
 4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the train is not the person eating pineapple##6
 8. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person eating pineapple##8
 9. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
10. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
11. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
12. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
13. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | adventure | spy        | scientific |
| Food   | lettuce | pumpkin   | tomato | pineapple     |
| Transport     | tram      | taxi      | train      | car        |

