1. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
2. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is cricket##7
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
4. the fan of pop is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
6. the person who's sport is handball is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the fan of jazz##1
8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person drinking fanta##7
9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
