 1. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 2. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
 3. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
 4. the person eating watermelon is not to the left of the person eating cabbage##8
 5. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
 7. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the person eating cranberry is not to the right of the person who growszinnia##8
11. the person eating watermelon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
