.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, musician, police-officer, teacher
House: modern, colonial, victorian, craftsman
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, subway, taxi, tram
 1. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
 2. the engineer is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the modern house##3
 4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the musician##1
 6. the police-officer is on the right of the engineer##1
 7. the teacher is the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the boat is not the musician##6
 9. the teacher is not to the left of the modern house##8
10. the modern house is not to the right of the musician##8
11. the police-officer is somewhere between the modern house and the person driving the boat##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4    |
| Job           | engineer  | police-officer | musician | teacher |
| House   | victorian | craftsman           | modern  | colonial |
| Transport     | boat      | taxi           | tram     | subway  |

