.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, russian
4 different games are played: chess, backgammon, canasta, go
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, handball, snowboarding, swimming
1. the person playing chess is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the colombian is not to the right of the person who's sport is handball##8
3. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person playing chess and the person playing go##2
4. the canadian is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the colombian is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
6. the person playing go is on the left of the russian##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is handball##7
8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person playing go##1
9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | colombian | canadian     | russian  | indonesian |
| Game           | backgammon      | go        | canasta   | chess |
| Sport         | handball  | snowboarding | swimming | golf       |

 